{"title":"球场剪影（图片）","authors":["江潭","徐启雄　苗地"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"球场剪影\t江潭诗  徐启雄　苗地画\t一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欧洲球坛老将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桌前稳重如山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日宝刀未老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威风不减当年。\t二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山鹰般矫健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞燕般轻盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬓云微动处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球出像流星。\t三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西非小将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身是胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲敌当前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颜色不变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能攻就攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能拦就拦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初生之犊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢轻看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球儿来得凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不慌又不忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"款款儿削，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳稳儿挡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起死回生好身手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赢得春雷阵阵响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼要明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手要快！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机不可失，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时不再来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁抓住战机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁就是胜者！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔如春波荡漾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"软如杨柳摆腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羡煞观众好眼福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未看赛球先看舞蹈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等得好镜头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累得满身汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"短短一段纪录片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得来岂等闲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一丝不苟看分明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分一分记得清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记分员的成绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记在观众的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}